Class RegexPattern

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.ephesoft.dcma.core.model.common.AbstractEntity
      • com.ephesoft.dcma.core.model.common.AbstractChangeableEntity
        • com.ephesoft.dcma.da.domain.RegexPattern
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    DomainEntity, EntityObject, java.io.Serializable

    public class RegexPattern
extends AbstractChangeableEntity
    The class RegexPattern represents a regex pattern. All regex patters learnt in Ephesoft, such as "\d{1,3}" with description "One to three digits", are implemented as instances of this class.

    1.0
